    m_LineSpacing: 1.2
  m_Text: The path of immortality encompasses all things, containing the stories of deities and immortals since the creation of the world by the Chinese. Players need to adventure through each story, and seal the monsters that appear in each story to obtain adventure rewards and the opportunity to continue the journey. When the player adventures through the final story, they will realize that looking back on their past experiences has been very rewarding, and the anticipation of the next story will truly be something they look forward to.
